{"tid":1174642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寵物是應該要絕育的，因為......","createTime":"2019-05-28T03:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T15:11:06.000Z","uid":197098,"like":28,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b9bf34316eabe3a17cf4af362f8398b859e41d4d","tid":1174642,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:55:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">根據愛護動物協會 和 美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 例如: 狗、兔子......絕育後會大大減少霸地盤，容易訓練去廁所。<br />\n<br />\n2. 荷爾蒙減少了會令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。<br />\n<br />\n3. 牠們是很容易患上生殖器疾病的動物，所以絕育也會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n4. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養)，因為好多動物一胎生十多個BB。<br />\n<br />\n5. 專家說絕育後才看到牠們真正本性，例如: 善良、懶惰、好動、活潑、親人......(有些活潑和親人，有些善良但懶惰等等)<br />\n<br />\n🐶🐱🐰🐕🐩🐇"},{"pid":"bcf41c883113bdedb8700fcd0db243172de5ea05","tid":1174642,"uid":54721,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"切左J就唔會有J病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f67e03ee3f7d866e56338ddd6e0023ce89da93c","tid":1174642,"uid":149357,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"bcf41c883113bdedb8700fcd0db243172de5ea05","tid":1174642,"uid":54721,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"切左J就唔會有J病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:09:21.000Z","msg":"絕育唔係切j喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />切蛋啊"},{"pid":"6fb0e4eb6b2ebff64c73224144a77d283b1fb2cd","tid":1174642,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45224a6ecd28705cce124cb26f5695a4b36dc524","tid":1174642,"uid":58335,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"咁講用係人身上一樣識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100fb3305f425d4442d5f85d2